  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This unit of assurance documents the credibility evidence for a CFD-based hemolysis prediction model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. The model has been applied in clinical research settings to inform ventricular assist device design decisions, and the assessment team has evaluated thirteen credibility factors under ASME V&V 40-2018 guidance. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across the operating envelope. All factors were reviewed against the model risk level and a consolidated credibility determination was reached by the responsible assessment team. The package conforms to the Minimal profile; structured context-of-use metadata is not encoded in this record.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cfd-hemolysis-absolute-prediction",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/morrison-cfd-centrifugal-pump-v3",
